up, you just end up not doing it, right?

69
00:04:32.350 --> 00:04:33.330
Gatsby builds that in.

70
00:04:33.330 --> 00:04:34.830
So now instead of wanting to do it and

71
00:04:34.830 --> 00:04:37.240
